text.tspan: So let's go ahead and do it!
Step 3: Select the slot to take from.
Step 4: Type in 1 again, as we are going to build
a Dyson Sphere around this star.
Step 5: Insert fuel into the drones so that they
can get to the launch pad.
Step 6: Do this for copper, iron, titanium, and
steel. I'll wait until you do so.
Hints: You can switch what the Magic Crates will
output, you will need to use both launch
pads, workers can move things for you.
